snippet.title: Treachery in Beatdown City: Ultra Remix Xbox Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore an angry city, meet the a huge array of the WORST people, and beat ‘em up with style! Pick your fighter, freeze time, build custom combos, and knock out your enemies, all to save the president.
Get ready to beat ‘em up in Treachery in Beatdown City Ultra Remix coming to on Xbox April 27th, 2023!
#idxbox #idatxbox #id_xbox
